It is safe for adults and children to use on troubled skin, face, scalp, hands, feet, hair, body, jock itch, and even vaginal dryness. It contains yellow sap, which gives the gel its golden yellow color, and is traditionally used for skin support. This gel is safe for burns, stretch marks, damaged and thinning hair, itchy scalp, after shave, as well as brushing your teeth. It contains skin nutrients and vitamins A, C, and E which are combined with chamomile and azulene extract sourced from Comfrey. The value of this aloe vera skin topical is tremendous. It’s easy to see why Cleopatra named aloe vera the beauty herb! Take your first steps towards a happier, healthier you today with Aloe Life Skin Gel. Aloe Life International Inc, a leader in the Aloe industry for over 30 years, was founded in 1991 by clinical nutritionist, researcher, and author Karen Masterson Koch. Her clinical experience and education in immunology working with the famous Dr. Virginia Livingston, MD, gave her a thirst for more research and natural health application. Studies at Dallas Fort Worth Medical University and other institutions around the globe on aloe vera launched her research into the whole leaf aloe vera concentrate which revealed amazing results and led to the very best - Aloe Life products!']

title_product: RoyalShave 3" Red Latigo Leather Straight Razor Strop
description: ['Royal Shave is proud to offer the best way to sharpen, align and polish the blade of your Straight Razor. Handcrafted in USA, our strop offers high quality materials without compromising on function and design. Upper Latigo Leather material is dual tanned using chrome and vegetable processes to create a pliable, yet strong and smooth surface for sharpening & re-aligning blades. A lower woven Nylon material is prime for removing debris before and polishing after completing passes over Latigo Leather. The top of the strop features a secure metal clip outfitted with a removable loop. The clip is designed to swivel, giving you complete control of your session. The opposing end of the strop is a long, leather handle area to keep hands safe when in use. Metal rivet-like fasteners tie all sections of the strop together, ensuring this essential tool will last. Quick Guide on How To Use: Secure the strop to a immovable object. A towel bar or robe hook is ideal. Remember that the strop must be pulled taught when in use. Lay the blade the Straight Razor flat against the leather and glide it toward you. Use light and even pressure. Then, twist your wrist to flip the blade over, keeping the spine of the glade against the leather. Keep the blade flat as you upstroke. Repeat toward and away passes about 40-50 times. Once complete, flip the strop so the webbed Nylon is the primary surface. Repeat same pass instructions about 3-5 times to clean and polish the blade. Total Length of Strop: 28.5” Total Length of Blade-Use Surface: 17.5” Total Width of Blade-Use Surface: 3”']

title_product: Waterpik Ultra Plus Water Flosser, Nano Flosser, Deluxe Traveler Case, Tip Storage Case and 12 Accessory Tips Combo Pack
description: ['-Ultra Plus features 10 pressure settings, improved water on/off switch on handle, and a contemporary design with chrome accents, 90-seconds of water capacity -In-lid storage to keep tips clean, 10 press settings for optimum control and customization -Nano water flosser features: Compact design perfect for travel in north America, energy efficient and quiet operation -Includes: 1 Ultra Plus water flosser - 1 recommended model by dental professionals, 1 Nano water flosser - 50% smaller than full-size models; 12 - Accessory Tips, 1 - Tip Storage Case, 1 - Nano Premium Travel Case  Product Benefits  -Can be used with your favorite mouthwash Ideal for braces and other dental work -Effective Plaque Removal: Removes up to 99.9% of plaque from treated areas Healthier Gums: Clinically proven up to 50% more effective for improving gum health vs. string floss Ideal for Implants: Clinically proven up to 2X as effective for improving gum health around implants vs. string floss using the Plaque Seeker tip Compatible With 120VAC/60Hz Outlets, For Use In North America Only LS-BB']
features:
['The Waterpik Ultra Plus (WP-150W) and Nano (WP-310W) Water Flosser combo pack is the perfect set of products to meet all of your Water Flossing needs. It includes the new and improved Ultra Plus Water Flosser and the Nano Water Flosser.'
 'The Waterpik Ultra Plus Water Flosser features 10 pressure settings, a contemporary design with chrome accents, improved on/off control on the handle, a covered reservoir with in-lid tip storage, and a high efficiency motor for superior performance and quieter operation.'
 'The Nano Water Flosser is 50% smaller than previous models with a reservoir that inverts for compact travel. It features a pressure control system with 3 settings, energy-efficient and quiet operation, and comes with a premium travel case.'
 'The Ultra Plus model includes a three-year warranty and the Nano model includes a two-year warranty. Both models are accepted by the American Dental Association (ADA) based on safety and effectiveness.']

title_product: Michael Malul OCEAN NOIR 3.4 EAU DE PARFUM NEWEST MEN
description: ['Bold and yet subtle, Ocean Noir envelopes anyone passing by in an air of mystery. He’s classically handsome, think tall, blue-eyed, broad shoulders, but there’s something mischievous about his smile. Miami-born and raised, he’s made quite a career for himself, however, that’s about as much as you can find out about him. An avid traveler, he’s hard to get to know as he’s yachting every weekend in some new exotic locale, blood & tan cocktail in hand. Tropical opening notes of marine mist, tangelo, and black coconut set a lush, mysterious tone as fresh mid notes of sea kelp, yarrow, and geranium pull you further out to sea. Deep and enduring base notes of amberwood, tonka bean, and musk take you from day to night.']

For a more fun and fragrant experience, personalize and enhance your Vanilla Bourbon EDP by generously spraying the Hair & Body Mist to refresh and deepen the scent, and take the Brush-On Fragrance Pen for on-the-go adventures and touch-ups. You may also layer and blend with other MIX:BAR fragrances to create your own signature scent! Experience MIX:BAR: MIX:BAR gives you a new way to express yourself through fragrance, with scents for every mood, attitude or occasion, all crafted by the finest perfumers. title_product: Studex Sterilized Piercing Earrings * Ear Stud * Reg. * S S * Studs * 12 Pair Individually Packaged. Great Buy, Gender Neutral Style, Locking Backs Should not Lose The Earrings
description: ["This product is designed to pierce the ear with the universal ear piercing instrument. They are packaged by the pair on plastic mounts and sterilized. Any product that pierces the skin is required by the AMA (AMERICAN MEDICAL ASSOCIATION) to be sterilized. Wearing gloves is not considered sterilization. Your hands cannot be sterilized. Any product that only touches the skin should be sanitized. The instrument is spring loaded and pierces the ear in a 10th of a second once the trigger is pulled. THE BLACK UNIVERSAL EAR PIERCING INSTRUMENT IS REQUIRED TO PIERCE THE EAR. The studs/styles used to pierce the ear are made out of surgical stainless steel (same material as a surgical instrument), which is also an AMA requirement. If the piercing stud is gold, it is 24 ct. gold that is electro- plated over the surgical steel. Electro-plating is a process where the gold is attached to the surgical steel with an electrical current in water. The bond is very strong and the gold should stay on for at least a year or longer. 24 ct. gold is the only gold that is pure and does contain nickel. Nickel is an alloy (Copper, iron, etc. are other examples) that is used to harden pure gold and metals. People have varying degrees of sensitivities to nickel and thus the 24 ct. (no nickel) should prevent sensitivities on a newly pierced ear. This training stud should be worn for 3-4 weeks without removal. At that time it should be replaced with a similar material (no nickel) earring. This replacement earring (can be interchanged) should be worn day and night for the following 4 months. The total healing time for a newly pierced ear is about 5-6 months. Very important, the replacement earrings for the 4 month period should be at least 14 ct. gold or higher. The advantage of using the Universal system is the cost. They generally range in the price range of $3 to $8 (Sally's Beauty Supply). THE RETAIL PRICE TO CHARGE THE EAR WITH THIS SYSTEM IS $20-$30."]

title_product: E'ARRS Jewelry Shield | Clear Protective Coating | L'Protect | 0.45 ounces | 1 Bottle
description: ["MADE IN THE USA. Apply to all metal surfaces that may come in contact with your skin (earrings, rings, watches, clasps, etc.). Apply a coat with the brush to a metal surface. Allow to dry for a least 30 minutes before touching or wearing and enjoy! Use fingernail polish remover to remove L’Protect. How does L'Protect differ from clear nail polish? This coating is different from clear nail polish as it is a lacquer specifically for metals. This formula is more similar to the clear coating that is put over the paint layers on cars formulated for use with jewelry and sensitive skin. This formula is intended to last longer without chipping as clear nail polish does. It does rub off over time but only requires a single, even coat to protect your skin and your jewelry. Additionally, though you can use nail polish remover to take the coating off, it creates a sticky glue glob instead of just rubbing off the surface. Ingredients: Methyl Ethyl Ketone, Isobutyl Acetate, 2-Propanol, Toluene, 2-Methyl-1-propanol, Xylene, Cellulose Nitrate, Tricresyl Phospahte, 2-Butoxyethyl, and Ethylbenzene."]
features:
["FOR SENSITIVE SKIN: Redness, itching, and green orblack piercings are caused by allergies to metals or reactions between skin acids and the metals in jewelry. L'Protect creates a barrier between metal and skin, preventing those irritations."
 "L'PROTECT JEWELRY SHIELD: Part of our Ear Care Solutions line, this product is a clear, brush-on coating that comes in a 0.45 fl. oz (13.5ml) bottle. It’s easy to keep in a jewelry box, on a dressing table, or to take with you on the go."
 'EASY TO USE: Clean & dry jewelry, then apply product to all metal surfaces that may contact skin. Allow to dry for at least 30 minutes. Then put on your jewelry! Reapply as needed. Product can be removed with nail polisher remover.'
 'PROTECT YOURSELF: This solution works to protect your skin against all metals. Use it on earrings, rings, bracelet and necklace clasps, as well as watches and eyeglasses'
 "E'ARRS INC.: Providing Quality Jewelry and Jewelry Solutions for everyday and all of life's big events! E’arrs Inc is a family-owned small business based in Gainesville, GA. We pride ourselves on providing jewelry and jewelry solutions that are Nickel-Free, Lead-Free, Cadmium-Free, and Cobalt-Free so that any pair of earrings or jewelry solution you try will be safe for any jewelry wearer."]

title_product: Bust Dust - Antiperspirant Powder for the Breasts and Chest
description: ['Nobody likes sweating through their bra or shirt. Unfortunately, due to genetics, heat, certain types of shirts, and a myriad of other factors, roughly 30% of people worldwide suffer from chest and breast sweating (Hyperhidrosis). While there have been many products on the market claiming to keep your chest fresh, none of them were actually an antiperspirant - simply baby powders with perfume. And without an antiperspirant component, these insufficient products will do nothing to stop wetness from leaking through your clothing. Bust Dust is a revolutionary product because it not only prevents odor, but also blocks sweat from exiting your skin, where applied. One jar of Bust Dust lasts the average person 2-3 months of use. Very light floral citrus scent. Directions: Apply generously to dry skin on chest, stomach, back or breasts. Ingredients: Aluminum Chlorohydrate 15% - Antiperspirant. Also contains: Corn Starch, Organic Lemon Powder, Allantoin, Mica Powder, Zinc Oxide, Titanium Dioxide, Bismuth Oxychloride, EDTA. Size: 1.5 OZ. Both jars include a sifter and puff.']
features:
['Fast-acting antiperspirant powder' 'Fights breast and chest sweating'
 'A great product for the back, neck, and face as well'
 'Comes in a light, fresh scent.'
 'Stop sweating through your shirt or bra!']

title_product: 32 Fl.oz Premium Argan Oil Moroccan Skin Nail Health Care Moisturizer
description:
['What is Argan Oil?'
 'Argan oil is pressed from the nut of the fruit of the Argan Tree, which is only found in Morocco. The argan tree lives to be about 150 to 200 years old and does not start producing the fruit until it is 30 to 50 years old. Because the tree is found only in a limited area, the oil itself is quite rare.'
 'Face Moisturizer - After cleansing morning and/or night, massage a few drops of argan oil directly onto your face and neck. Since argan is considered a dry oil, it absorbs quickly and is not greasy. If you want to use it as a serum, apply your night cream after the oil absorbs into the skin. Hydrating Toner – Add a few drops of argan oil to your favorite facial toner to hydrate and tone simultaneously. You can make your own toner by adding a few drops of argan oil to Rose or Orange Blossom water. Rejuvenating & Brightening Face Mask – Add a few drops of argan oil to your store-bought mask. Alternatively, make your own mask by mixing 1 tablespoon of lemon juice, 3 teaspoons of Greek-style yogurt, 1 tablespoon of honey and 3 drops of argan oil in a bowl. Apply on a clean, dry face and leave on for 10 minutes. Rinse off with warm water. Face Glow – Add a drop or two of argan oil to your foundation, bronzer or tinted moisturizer for a dewy, luminous glow. Leave-on Conditioner – After the shower, while your hair is still wet, add a few drops of argan oil to your hair, ends and scalp to hydrate and moisturize. It’s especially nourishing if your hair is dry from daily use of a blow dryer, straight-iron or curling iron. Hair Styling Shine – When your hair is dry, use as a styling product by adding a few drops of argan oil to the palms of your hand. Rub your hands together and run your fingers through your hair to create shine and tame frizz. You only need a small amount.']
features:
['Hair: Argan oil is a great product to calm frizzy ends, add moisture to dry hair as well as add a little shine. Apply to your hair while it is still damp for an all over treatment or apply just to your dry ends after your hair is dry.'
 "Scalp: If you're dealing with dry scalp, apply some argan oil to a cotton ball and dab your scalp with the oil. If you do this before bed, you'll give the oil plenty of time to moisturize your scalp before you wash your hair in the morning."
 "Face: It might seem scary to apply a pure oil to your face, especially if you have finicky skin, but we have been doing just that and our skin is completely turning around. It's smooth, clear and radiant, all thanks to using argan oil as our daily morning moisturizer."
 'Body: You can use argan oil for a full body moisturizer, applying just as you would a body lotion or cream. Apply the oil right after you get out of your shower for best moisturizing results.'
 'Hands: Argan oil is a great oil to use on your hands, especially on your cuticles and on your nails if they are prone to cracking and peeling.']

description:
['Why do you need this makeup brush cleaner:'
 'In fact, your makeup brushes are much more dirty than imagine. Makeup brushes should be cleaned at least twice per month, not only to remove residual cosmetics, oil, dirt and dead skin as well.'
 'This cleaner can help you clean your all size makeup brushes more easier.'
 'Just take 10 seconds, \xa0we can clean it thoroughly. And another 10 seconds, we dry it as new.'
 'How to use it:'
 '1.\xa0Put some water and soap or makeup cleaning shampoo into the bowl.'
 '2. Find the suitable collars and insert the brush into the spinner.'
 '3. Dip and dunk the brush in the liquid.'
 '4. Turn on the spinner, spin the brush to clean.'
 '5. Change the water and clean again.' '6. Spin the brush to dry it.'
 'Package including:' '1 x Brush Cleaner' '1 x Attachment spindle'
 '1 x Brush Spinner Bowl' '1 x Silicone seal and splash guard ring'
 '8 x Rubber Holders(different sizes)' '1 x User Manual' 'NOTE:'
 'The machine is power by 2 X AAA battery\xa0(not included the battery)']

 'TOP QUALITY MATERIALS - Made from high grade materials to ensure long-lasting use. And it is nontoxic, environmental friendly and easy cleaning.'
 'PACKAGE INCLUDED - Brush Spinner, Eight Rubber Holders, Plastic Bowl, Bowl Splash Guard Ring and Manual.'
 'QUALITY GUARANTEE - We offer 30 days money back guarantee to ensure complete satisfaction & risk free.']

title_product: Wrinkle Butter Anti-Aging Night Cream Hydrates Skin and Boost Collagen for Psoriasis and Eczema with Earthworm Pooh Extract
description: ['Wrinkle Butter reduces wrinkles and boosts collagen production for increased elasticity. It\'s also an effective remedy for psoriasis, eczema and dry skin. Wrinkle Butter uses a special extract made from earthworm poop, known to organic farmers as "Earthworm Castings". These castings make plants grow larger and extend their life cycles by energizing stem cells with an array of powerful anti-aging compounds. Those same organic compounds produce similar anti-aging effects when applied to human skin. Earthworm castings contain large concentrations of humates, auxins, kinetins and cytokinins that are found in the most expensive $100 plus anti-aging products. This cream also contains Capsaicin and Caffeine to boost topical circulation and absorption. There is no scent except the slight aroma of the organic Shea and Cocoa butter used in the natural cream base. Earthworm Wrinkle Butter was featured on The Doctors TV Show and in FIRST for Women Magazine.']

description: ["Yes To Cucumbers Hypoallergenic Facial Wipes gently remove dirt, sweat and makeup (eye makeup too!) without the need to rinse. Whether you're out and about, going for a run, or having a late night, these wipes make it a snap to refresh on-the-go. Packed with green superfoods these all-natural, biodegradable wipes naturally refresh and rejuvenate all-in-one. Stay gorgeous, and go from zero to clean in seconds! Snap up the lid and snatch out a towelette! Gently glide across your face and neck. Feel refreshed? You should- your skin is clean, revitalized and nourished- in just a snap! These 95% natural, oil-free, non-comedogenic, hypoallergenic wipes are made with compostable, FSC certified fabric. They are petroleum free, SLS free, paraben free, and cruelty-free. Say Yes to Cucumbers Hypoallergenic Facial Wipes! These 2 pack wipes are specifically sold by the manfucaturer. We can&rsquo. INGREDIENTS Water, Glycerin, Cucumis Sativas (Cucumber) Extract, Aloe Barbadensis (Aloe) Extract, Camellia Sinensis (Green Tea) Extract, Sodium Chloride (Sea Salt), Carpylyl/Capryl Glucoside, Guar Hydroxypropyltrimonium Chloride, Polyglyceryl-4 Caprate, Caprylic/Capric Triglyceride, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate, Citric Acid, Phenoxyethanol, Fragrance."]

description:
['PROFESSIONAL QUALITY MADE TO LAST:'

 'JNxcel Capes' 'are also great for do-it-yourself at home haircutting.'
 'JNxcel Salon Products'
 ', a small family-run business, has been manufacturing and supplying these quality shampoo, hair cutting and hair styling capes to the professional beauty salon/spa and barber shop industry for over 20 years.'
 'SIZED TO FIT EVERY CLIENT:'
 'These generously-sized 48 inches wide by 60 inches long capes (approximate) feature 8 closely-spaced quality rust-proof stainless steel snaps. More snaps, better quality snaps, and more closely-spaced snaps (1-inch apart) than most other capes. This ensures a snug and comfortable fit on every neck from 10 to 24 inches, perfect for every client who sits in your chair. They will fit a small child as well as a very large man, and everyone in-between.'
 'BINDING vs. SIMPLE HEM FOR STYLE:'
 'Instead of a simple unfinished-looking hem, these' 'JNxcel Capes'
 'have a 1/2 inch tightly stitched binding sewn around the complete edge of the cape and the corners are rounded for a smooth clean look and long lasting durability.'
 'CARE INSTRUCTIONS:'
 'Simply wipe clean, or machine wash with cool water and dry with low heat to extend the life of the water repellency. Commercial dryers are not recommended as the heat setting may be too hot. A Loop has been sewn onto the cape for ease of hanging for drying or storage purposes.'

title_product: Makeup Cleansing Wipes- GreenTea/ AloeVera/ VitaminC/ Cucumber
description: ['Cleansing Makeup Removal Wipes Bulk - Great for travel toiletries - 120 Count (4-Pack) (Aloe Vera & Green Tea)Pattern Name:Aloe Vera & Green TeaOur Makeup Cleansing Wipes nourish skin while removing face & eye makeup, even waterproof mascara. This formulation helps to condition and soothe skin- it leaves no greasy residue and is hypoallergenic. Cucumber Extract naturally soothes skin, and eases puffiness and swelling. These premoistened soft wipes cool and soothe on contact, to replenish delicate skin around the eyes and face. Our formulation leaves no greasy residue and is hypoallergenic. A convenient way to daily cleanse, stimulate and beautify your skin & body. Aloe Vera is a short, cactus-like plant that grows in hot, dry regions. Its extract has long been prized for its health & beauty benefits. Aloe Vera helps reduce fine wrinkles around the eyes. Its anti-aging properties help maintain collagen of the skin and also help stimulate collagen formation to restore skin suppleness. In addition, Aloe Vera is a good moisturizer and emollient, as it helps hydrate the skin. Use daily to stimulate and beautify your skin & body. Green Tea: Our Makeup Cleansing Wipes nourish skin while removing face & eye makeup, even waterproof mascara. This formulation helps to condition and soothe skin- it leaves no greasy residue and is hypoallergenic. Green Tea has traditionally been known to contain powerful antioxidants and moisturizers. We have formulated it into a soothing, skin-nourishing cleansing wipe. When used daily, it helps reduce the look of dryness, wrinkles and sagging. Apply the pre-moistened wipes to your face, neck, or anywhere you wish to support healthy skin tone, firmness and appearance. Vitamin C: Our unique blend of ingredients contains Vitamin-C, which is a strong antioxidant with light whitening effect. Vitamin-C stimulates collagen synthesis and activates skin cell regeneration. Our pre-moistened wipes leaves your skin feeling soft, smooth and radiant.']

title_product: Crave Extreme For Men EDP - Eau De Parfum 100ml(3.4 oz) | Pepper, Calabrian Bergamot, Elemi, Vetiver, Pink Pepper, Sichuan Pepper, Patchouli, Lavender, Geranium, Cedar, Ambroxan & Labdanum | Perfume, Perfumes for men, Men's fragrances, Fragrance, Men's eau de parfum | by Intense Elite
features:
['BLEND: A masculine lighter occidental fragrance, which is perfect if you want a memorable perfume without it being too strong or intense. It is floral and smells beautiful, indulgent, and luxurious. It is accentuated with the spicy notes of Pepper and Calabrian Bergamot proceeded with a multifaceted scent of Elemi, Vetiver, Pink Pepper, Sichuan Pepper, Patchouli, Lavender, and Geranium. All these ending on a sweet-earthy, woody, musky combination of Cedar, Ambroxan, and Labdanum.'
 'OCCIDENTAL: The occidental compositions draw their richness and sophistication from precious substances such as Amber, spices like Pink Pepper and Sichuan Pepper, exotic woods of Vetiver, Patchouli, Labdanum and Cedar. These warm, dry and elegant masculine accords contain a dash of Calabrian Bergamot and Aromatic notes of Lavender.'
 'CITRUS: This fragrance is mainly composed of citrus notes such as Calabrian bergamot characterized by its freshness and lightness. The masculine character comes from the frequently strong presence of aromatic and spicy notes of Pink Pepper and Sichuan Pepper.'
 'WOODY: The woody middle note, are warm and opulent when based on sandalwood or patchouli, Cedar and vetiver make them dryer. Crave Extreme For Men is for the man who wants the perfect moment to last forever.'
 'CHYPRE: The woody accords of Vetiver, Cedar, form the core of these compositions for Men. The addition of chypre notes such as labdanum enhances the predominant woody accord of crave extreme.'
 'SILLAGE & PERFORMANCE: Illuminated by Pink Pepper, Sichuan Pepper and sweet floral Geranium and Lavender, it smells great. The trail left by Crave Extreme For Men in wake of its wearer has a very long-lasting effect. It has a great sillage rating while it stays close to the skin.'
 'BOTTLE: Crave Extreme For Men was designed giving the masterful attention to every aspect of development and packaging that lures the consumer into the luxurious cosmos of the fragrance captured within the bottle.'
 'TOP NOTES: Pepper, Calabrian Bergamot'
 'MIDDLE NOTES: Elemi, Vetiver, Pink Pepper, Sichuan Pepper, Patchouli, Lavender, Geranium'
 'BASE NOTES: Cedar, Ambroxan, Labdanum']
